5. What are different types of lists in HTML? With Example.\b0\par
-There are three types of lists in HTML: ordered lists, unordered lists, and definition lists.\par
- Ordered lists use numbers or letters to indicate the order of the list items. Example: \par
<ol>\par
  <li>Item 1</li>\par
